Package ba.unsa.etf.rpr.controllers

Class AdminFlightsController

java.lang.Object
ba.unsa.etf.rpr.controllers.AdminFlightsController
public class AdminFlightsController extends Object
The class AdminFlightsController is responsible for handling the administration of flights. It provides methods for adding, editing and deleting flights, as well as displaying a list of all flights.
